text:
Thank you <@UBT0AHWLD> for helping me solve this! We changed the CTA style from the button preset to “Link (No Style)” so it’s only the link.
From there, we copied and pasted button CSS from this tool to have it apply as needed to our site: <https://www.clickminded.com/button-generator/>
To add the hover effect, we added:
.&lt;CSS-Custom Class-Name&gt;:hover {
  background-color: #C2571D !important;
}
